<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<e:Skin class="skins.ButtonSkin" states="up,down,disabled" minHeight="50" minWidth="100"
        xmlns:e="http://ns.egret.com/eui">

    <e:Image id="down" width="100%" height="100%" includeIn="down" source="dft_json.dft_rct_png" />

             textAlign="center" />
